{"title": "吐比卡瓦希普族", "index": 3, "content": [{"type": "text", "value": "吐比卡瓦希普族"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_ba18753630.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "在皮门塔布沿诺河从事调查"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_cdb87cc1ee.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "蒙蝶村的田园"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_b93311c072.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "在蒙蝶村的空地上"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_3ed8a7bb36.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "蒙蝶村男子用硬树脂制成的唇塞"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_f5240e1f86.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "蒙蝶村圆形小屋内观"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_7df1258158.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "蒙蝶人射箭，请注意右手的姿势（“地中海式”），与波洛洛族及南比克瓦拉族的姿势（美洲常用的姿势）不同"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_c1d5c211bc.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "两位蒙蝶族母亲"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_a89809a1b3.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "蒙蝶族妇女与她的孩子（小孩双眉涂胶，等胶硬后，连眉毛一起拔掉）"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_075864f383.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "小母猴鲁西达"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_2568a8ad59.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "与吐比卡瓦希普族在马查多河边扎营"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_a5eca6dcf6.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "吐比卡瓦希普族人（帕廷）剥猴子（他戴阳具护套，腰系皮带，皮带是新得的礼物）"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_2cb3df9f96.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "吐比卡瓦希普族酋长塔培拉希"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_7f5722f0d4.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "塔培拉希的妻子昆哈津带着孩子"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_3e8c462190.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "普塔培卫拉累希札的儿子"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_02e669ffad.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "偏哈娜：一对兄弟共同的妻子"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_360de2a574.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "吐比卡瓦希普族老者"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/b146b56d2718/image/b146b56d2718_570c613ee0.webp", "alt": "picture"}, {"type": "text", "value": "顺帕拉那河而下遇到激流，搬船而行"}]}